
Comment:  Which P-flag and Mask-bits to set when a player changes status...
Comment:  The higher levels inherit bits from lower.

PflagApprentice:
  Exorcise Zap Resurrect Stats Goto WreckDoors Reset
  SummonObj Weather Lock Trace Peace NoHassle TitleEdit Emote;

PflagWizard:
  NoTrace NoSnoop NoZap NoSummon NoSteal NoMagic NoForce NoAlias MflagEdit
  ObjectEdit Heal AliasMob StartInvis RoomEdit Clone Punt Timeout Load/Store 
  Echo NoExorcise NoBurn Burn Sic ShowUsers;

MaskWizard:
  NoExorcise;

PflagProphet:
  Raw ChScore ChLevel;

PflagArchWizard:
  UAFInfo PflagEdit AliasPlayers Frob ChMobData Syslog PZap;

MaskArchWizard:
  NoPunt;

PflagAvatar:
  SflagEdit Shutdown Probation;

PflagGod:
  MaskEdit IgnoreNoAt NoPunt NoForget EflagEdit TextRaw Snoop SeeUser
  NoSic CanLog FList NflagEdit ChatMod Socket NoTimeOut SeeIdle SeeSocket
  ViewCom Ban Settime;

MaskGod:
  IgnoreNoAt;

PflagMaster:
  Reboot Signal;
